  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComponentCallbacks, ComponentCallbacks2, DrawerLayout.DrawerListener, KeyEvent.Callback, LayoutInflater.Factory, LayoutInflater.Factory2, View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, Window.Callback

    public abstract class NavigationDrawerActivity
extends SprocketsActivity
implements DrawerLayout.DrawerListener
    Manages the ActionBar during navigation drawer events according to the Android design guidelines. See NavigationDrawerToggle for details on how the ActionBar is affected and your responsibilities in onCreateOptionsMenu methods.

    Subclasses must call setDrawerLayout before onPostCreate runs.

    If your Activity includes components that may start an ActionMode, they should implement ActionModePresenter and be provided in getActionModePresenters().
